* Table based CRC calculation routine
*
* Zero out CRC and CRC+1 before calling first time.
* Call once for each byte to add to the CRC.
* Trashes A and X. Executes in 28 cycles.
* (with CRC and CRC+1 on zero page)

CRCCALC EOR CRC+1 ;add byte into crc hi byte
 TAX ;to make offset into tables
 LDA CRC ;get previous lo byte back
 EOR TABLEHI,X ;add it to the proper table entry
 STA CRC+1 ;save it
 LDA TABLELO,X ;get new lo byte
 STA CRC ;save it back
 RTS ;all done

* crc-16 table

